about a thousand dollars for, uh...

11:11.212 --> 11:13.590
...Africa or Tibet,
one of those starving places.

11:13.756 --> 11:16.885
Anyway, you should go. Tyler...

11:17.969 --> 11:19.892
I'd like you to meet Elissa.

11:20.054 --> 11:21.601
- Have fun.
- Yeah.

11:25.393 --> 11:27.111
- Hey.
- Hi.

11:27.270 --> 11:29.568
Sorry about my mom.
She gave you the full treatment?

11:29.731 --> 11:33.201
Oh, no worries. Moms are like that.
I'm sure you're really a total loser.

11:33.359 --> 11:34.736
(CHUCKLES)

11:35.945 --> 11:39.575
- Do you want to go for a swim?
- No. it's fine. I'll watch.

11:40.533 --> 11:41.659
All right.

11:42.076 --> 11:45.296
- Whoo!
- (CHILDREN SCREAM)

11:45.455 --> 11:47.799
- BOY: Marco!
- GIRL: Polo!

11:47.957 --> 11:49.584
- Marco!
- Polo!

11:49.751 --> 11:52.595
- WOMAN: So, how are you settling in?
- SARAH: Good. Good.

11:52.754 --> 11:54.552
