14:27.950 --> 14:29.247
Just assuring my friends back home

14:29.410 --> 14:31.754
I'm not hanging myself
from a shower rod.

14:31.913 --> 14:35.292
Well, if you're looking
for something less morbid...

14:35.458 --> 14:37.586
...our famine relief group is meeting
after school today.

14:37.752 --> 14:39.925
You want to come?
I can give you a ride after if you want.

14:40.088 --> 14:42.682
Oh, I can't. I'm going to watch
a movie tonight with my mom.

14:42.840 --> 14:44.433
Too bad.

14:44.592 --> 14:46.060
- (PHONE RINGS)
- Hang on, one sec.

14:47.720 --> 14:48.972
- Hi.
- SARAH: Hi, honey.

14:49.138 --> 14:51.982
How was school?
Is your soul still intact?

14:52.141 --> 14:53.484
Relatively. How about you?

14:53.643 --> 14:57.364
Um, OK. But they stuck me
with the night shift.

14:57.522 --> 14:58.774
Already?

14:58.940 --> 15:01.193
It's just my first day,
so I can't really say no.

15:01.359 --> 15:02.952
But I'm not going to be home before ten.

15:03.111 --> 15:08.459
It's fine. Tyler invited me to this...
famine relief group thing,

15:08.616 --> 15:09.993
so I'll just see you when I get home.

15:10.159 --> 15:12.412
Oh, that's great.
Don't do anything I wouldn't do.

15:12.578 --> 15:14.296
- Bye.
- Bye.

15:15.957 --> 15:18.130
- Well, I guess I can go.
- Cool.

15:18.292 --> 15:20.511
(HIP-HOP PLAYS)

15:20.670 --> 15:23.093
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

15:23.256 --> 15:25.634
- Hey.
- Tyler, what's up?

15:26.843 --> 15:29.562
- So this is famine relief?
- Yeah.

15:29.720 --> 15:32.815
Last year we gave 1200 dollars
to Stop Hunger Now.

15:32.974 --> 15:34.692
It just came straight off
my dad's Optima card,

15:34.851 --> 15:37.730
rather than waiting in store parking
lots and begging people for change.

15:37.895 --> 15:41.866
Put it on our college apps
as community service.

15:42.024 --> 15:46.404
Wow. I have to admit
a certain smarmy brilliance.

15:48.531 --> 15:50.829
(HIP-HOP PLAYS)

16:01.836 --> 16:03.383
- (MUFFLED MUSIC CONTINUES)
- (KNOCKING)

16:03.546 --> 16:05.139
- ELISSA: ls anybody in here?
- (DOOR OPENS)

16:07.341 --> 16:09.719
- Oh, I'm sorry.
- (MOANS SOFTLY)

16:12.597 --> 16:14.349
(MOANS)

16:14.515 --> 16:15.983
Are you OK?

16:16.601 --> 16:19.855
Yeah, I just need to rest.

16:20.813 --> 16:22.907
(MOANS)

16:33.868 --> 16:35.711
(MOANS)

16:42.502 --> 16:44.345
