- (VOMITING)

16:44.504 --> 16:47.428
So I'll just wait to pee.

16:47.590 --> 16:49.183
TYLER: There you are.

16:51.761 --> 16:53.729
- Hi.
- Hi.

16:56.724 --> 16:59.273
