17:01.437 --> 17:04.941
- What? I'm joking. Come here.
- No.

17:05.107 --> 17:06.279
- Come here. Come here.
- I don't...

17:06.442 --> 17:08.319
- Tyler, stop.
- Come on.

17:08.486 --> 17:10.829
