17:10.988 --> 17:12.830
What's your problem?

17:12.990 --> 17:14.287
Asshole.

17:18.079 --> 17:22.128
(THUNDER RUMBLES)

17:35.972 --> 17:38.771
(CAR APPROACHING)

17:57.118 --> 17:59.246
(DIALING)

18:02.999 --> 18:06.469
This is Sarah, I'm not here right now,
leave me a message.

18:18.973 --> 18:20.225
Hey, do you need a ride?

18:20.391 --> 18:23.395
