18:24.520 --> 18:27.023
No, it's not. I saw you move in
on Sycamore Lane.

18:29.400 --> 18:31.152
I live next door.

18:32.820 --> 18:35.118
It looks like it's going to rain.
Can I give you a ride?

18:35.281 --> 18:37.283
No. I'm fine with walking.

18:39.535 --> 18:42.004
You're ten miles from home,
let me give you a ride.

18:42.163 --> 18:44.962
No really, I'm totally fine.
I'm waiting for my mom.

18:46.167 --> 18:47.589
OK.

18:52.715 --> 18:56.436
(RAIN PATTERING)

18:59.221 --> 19:03.397
- Shit.
- (THUNDER CRASHES)

19:05.853 --> 19:07.730
(MOANS)

19:22.453 --> 19:26.424
(MUSIC PLAYS SOFTLY ON RADIO)

19:44.308 --> 19:45.730
Your parents got killed.

19:48.979 --> 19:51.232
I'm sorry. I know the people
were talking about it,

19:51.399 --> 19:54.073
and I knew I shouldn't say...
I'm going to shut up now.

19:54.235 --> 19:55.737
It's OK.

19:57.279 --> 19:59.452
You just said
what you were thinking.

20:00.950 --> 20:03.453
