Carrie Anne?

25:39.913 --> 25:41.790
Don't I look after you?

25:46.795 --> 25:49.298
Listen, we have a new neighbor, OK?

25:50.340 --> 25:52.638
Her name is Elissa.

25:52.801 --> 25:54.599
Her and her mom just moved
into the Reeds' house.

25:54.762 --> 25:57.811
And I want you to leave her alone,
you understand me?

25:59.183 --> 26:00.901
Yeah.

27:11.213 --> 27:12.886
Bitch.

27:16.009 --> 27:17.556
GIRL: Hey.

27:17.719 --> 27:18.686
Elissa, right?

27:18.846 --> 27:20.894
-Yeah.
