and I got sick

27:30.566 --> 27:32.944
all over Caitlin's bath towels
and she threw a fit.

27:33.110 --> 27:35.704
Who are these people,
why are you friends with them?

27:36.613 --> 27:39.082
I don't know. I mean...

27:39.241 --> 27:42.245
I used to go out with Tyler,
but he's kind of a dick.

27:42.411 --> 27:44.129
