27:47.040 --> 27:51.591
- Hm.
- Oh, hey. Jake.

27:51.753 --> 27:54.848
Elissa, this is my brother Jake
and his best friend, Robbie.

27:55.007 --> 27:56.384
You guys, this is Elissa.

27:56.550 --> 27:59.770
Yeah, I've been wanting to meet you.
You were in a band.

27:59.928 --> 28:02.022
- How did you know...
- Oh. Google.

28:02.181 --> 28:04.604
Nothing is sacred anymore, right?
Everything's online.

28:04.766 --> 28:07.485
Anyway, we have
the Battle of the Bands coming up.

28:10.314 --> 28:11.691
So, what do you say?

28:11.857 --> 28:14.110
- You want to come sing with us?
